		<font color="#0c437b"><font size=+1>
		<b>The Company</b></font></font><br><br>
		
		Mobile Mini, Inc. is the dominant leader in the design and manufacture of quality, 
		high security, all steel, portable storage units and custom structures.<br><br>
		
		The Company's fundamental mission is to solve the storage industries needs by 
		providing the industry with safe, secure, weather resistant storage containers.
		<br><br>
		
		The combination of portability and security is enabling Mobile Mini to effectively 
		meet the needs of virtually all storage customers ranging from homeowners needing 
		storage between homes, to Fortune 500 companies needing record storage, to 
		telecommunications companies needing custom units to house complex communication 
		equipment at remote sites.<br><br>
		
		Since 1983, Mobile Mini has helped solve the storage needs of tens of thousands of 
		customers across the United States.<br><br>
		
		<font color="#0c437b"><font size=+1>
		<b>An Overview</b><br><br></font></font>
		
		<b>Branch and Dealer Network</b><br><br>
		
		Mobile Mini currently markets its products through 8 company branch locations in 
		Arizona, California and Texas and 51 dealers throughout the United States and 
		Canada. Each branch and 
		<a href="dealer.html">dealer</a> location sells, rents and leases 
		<a href="storage.html">
		storage containers</a> and <a href="storage.html">custom structures</a>.<br><br>
		
		<b>Telecommunication</b><br><br>
		
		The <a href="telecomm.html">Mobile Telestructures</a> division designs and fabricates 
		shelters used to house telecommunications equipment for cellular / PCS sites. 
		This division also offers an array of specialty products to this industry including 
		cell-on-wheels (COW), equipment cabinets, and generator rooms.<br><br>
		
